Package: rclone-service-tray
Version: 1.0.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Rclone Service Tray contributors
Depends: python3, python3-pyside6.qtcore, python3-pyside6.qtgui, python3-pyside6.qtwidgets, systemd
Recommends: rclone
Description: System tray manager for rclone mounts
 Rclone Service Tray monitors and manages rclone mount services controlled by
 systemd user units from a KDE-compatible system tray application.
